data.text: @BrianIsSuperRad Sounds like an incredible stomach ache

@BrianIsSuperRad @itsjessipashia If anything, Halloween for me has the best thing in this quagmire of a year, trying to fit all the fun stuff in before the 31st is quite the challenge, but I think we're up to the task 😎🎃

@OverlordViper @itsjessipashia I didn't even name off carving pumpkins, decorating, watching horror movies, special Halloween eps of shows, bonfires, pumpkin spice everything, etc. There's so much to enjoy!

@BrianIsSuperRad @itsjessipashia I agree, seen people saying they're 'done with Halloween' weeks before even the big lead-up to it which is baffling to me. I'm having a blast just watching movies & enjoying decorations. Still hype for #HalloweenMovie and that Nightmare 🍔🍟

@OverlordViper @itsjessipashia It's so odd, as I've seen so many people calling this Halloween season a disappointment. There's so much cool stuff out there. It's been an incredibly difficult year and it's all helped me keep me keep my head above water.
@BrianIsSuperRad I want this thread to go on forever 🤗 so glad Halloween was there when you @itsjessipashia and your family needed it most! 🎃
